n]] * [[Neil Simon]] <!-- – humorous playwright --> * [[H. Allen Smith]] * [[Jill Sobule]] * [[Ed Subitzky]] * [[Julia Sweeney]] * [[Jonathan Swift]] * [[Herbert Tarr]] * [[Jeremy Taylor (singer)|Jeremy Taylor]] * [[William Tenn]] * [[Larry Thompson (humorist)|Larry Thompson]] * [[Thomas Bangs Thorpe]] * [[James Thurber]] * [[John Kennedy Toole]] * [[Calvin Trillin]] * [[Mark Twain]] * [[Aisha Tyler]] * [[Brian Unger]] * [[Peter Ustinov]] * [[Kurt Vonnegut]] * [[Sarah Vowell]] * [[Artemus Ward]] * [[Sam Watkins|Sam. R. Watkins]] * [[Bill Watterson]] * [[Ellis Weiner]] * [[E.B. White]] * [[Oscar Wilde]] * [[Marshall P. Wilder]] * [[Justin Wilson (chef)|Justin Wilson]] * [[Robert Wringham]] * [[P. G. Wodehouse]] }}
